parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the airbag is designed to provide crucial protection to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Airbag failure to deploy in the event of a crash
airbag warning light illuminating
airbag housing splitting or cracking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag malfunction can lead to unintended deployment, which can cause injuries or accidents, or failure to deploy in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag deploys unnecessarily
airbag fails to deploy in the event of a crash
airbag warning light illuminating
airbag housing splitting or cracking.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure Leading to Vehicle Fire
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause a vehicle fire, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks
the battery light comes on
a loud pop is heard
smoke is seen
and the vehicle becomes engulfed in fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling or shut down can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine shuts down without warning
the vehicle stalls on the road
the vehicle dies and will not restart for a period of time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel system issues can cause engine stalling, loss of power, or difficulty restarting the vehicle.
symptoms: The vehicle dies when the gas tank is near empty
the gas gauge dial wavers from side to side
the vehicle will not restart for a period of time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Exhaust system failure can cause engine damage, decreased performance, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The exhaust manifold cracks
resulting in engine damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly accelerates out of control
resulting in a collision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine hose failure can cause engine damage, decreased performance, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Engine hoses need to be repaired or replaced due to failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, as the vehicle surges forward unexpectedly.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and uncontrollably
the throttle sticks
the engine surges unexpectedly
the brake does not respond
the vehicle accelerates out of control when engaged in drive or reverse gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the accelerator cable can cause unintended acceleration, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: The accelerator cable rubs against the air conditioning line
causing a hole and releasing freon into the air.
